  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis: navigated revision total knee arthroplasty results in a more precise
      reconstruction of preoperatively planned joint line than conventional revision total knee
      arthroplasty (rTKA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
